# AI Prompts Used for SEO Content

## Prompt A – Pillar Blog Outline
You are an expert SEO writer. Create a detailed blog outline for a dental clinic website.
Business: Dental Clinic
Location: Bangalore
Primary Keyword: Best Dental Clinic in Bangalore
Requirements:
1. Include H1, H2, H3 headings
2. Add internal linking suggestions for supporting blogs
3. Include meta description (150–160 characters)
4. Focus on local SEO (city + service naturally)
5. Make headings keyword-rich

## Prompt B – Supporting Blog Content
You are an SEO content writer creating a supporting blog for a dental clinic.
Main Pillar: Best Dental Clinic in Bangalore
Supporting Blog Topic: [Insert Supporting Keyword]
Requirements:
1. Write 500–700 words
2. Include H2 and H3 headings
3. Focus on local SEO (city + service keywords)
4. Include conclusion with business CTA (call to action)
5. Include internal link to main pillar blog

## Prompt C – Local SEO Adaptation
Rewrite the blog content to naturally include local SEO references: city name, neighborhoods, and service-related keywords.
Make it fully human-readable and optimized for Google.
